Lola Naymark https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lola_Naymark 0 Lola Naymark (born 5 April 1987) is a French film and television actress. In 2005 she was nominated for the César Award for Most Promising Actress for her role in A Common Thread, but lost to Sara Forestier.
